umbia_University_alumni" title="Category:Columbia University alumni">Columbia University alumni</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:United_States_Secretaries_of_State" title="Category:United States Secretaries of State">United States Secretaries of State</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Politicians_from_New_York_(state)" title="Category:Politicians from New York (state)">Politicians from New York (state)</a></li></ul></div></div>
